## ðŸš€ Installation

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.8 or higher
- C++ compiler (for building OR-Tools extension)
- OR-Tools library

### Step 1: Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/vaithak/TSP-all-pair-shortest.git
cd TSP-all-pair-shortest
```
